article.description: — Malevy Leons scored 32 points to lead Bradley over Merrimack 83-41 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Leons scores 32, Bradley takes down Merrimack 83-41
article.linkText: Leons scores 32, Bradley takes down Merrimack 83-41
article.story: PEORIA, Ill. -- — Malevy Leons scored 32 points to lead Bradley over Merrimack 83-41 on Saturday night. Leons added 10 rebounds, three steals, and three blocks for the Braves (4-3). Connor Hickman added 14 points with four 3-pointers and Rienk Mast finished with 12 points. Jordan Derkack led the Warriors (1-6) in scoring, finishing with 13 points and three steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
